body.description: This beautiful deluxe 4-piece expandable luggage set is manufactured with a patented heavy duty EVA-molded hi-count fabric. This set is perfect for the serious and experienced traveler! Manufactured with the very best heavy duty polyester and PVC backing, this luggage set is designed for the traveler on the go and comes with three expandable uprights and a flight tote bag. It comes packed with features including: an inside retractable handle, EZ-Roll in-line skate wheels, back zippered secured pockets, top and side comfort grip handle, stability bars at the bottom to avoid tilting, and locks with keys. Upright features include: Clear in-line skate wheel system for smooth ride Push-button self-locking internally stored retractable handle system Ergonomic and comfortable padded top and side grip handles Two front full size zipper-secured pockets Three internal organizational pockets for all your traveling needs Each upright's interior is fully lined with a durable and elegantly imprinted lining Elegant silver pewter heavy duty industrial hardware Carry-On Flight Tote Bag features include: Elegantly imprinted full interior lining Detachable and adjustable non-slip shoulder strap Spacious main compartment Maximum strength industrial hardware 19-inch Carry-on Upright: 20 inches high x 12. 5 inches wide x 7. 5 inches expandable to 10 inches deep. 6 lbs. 24-inch Upright: 24 inches high x 16 inches wide x 10 inches expandable to 12 inches deep. 8 lbs. 28-inch Upright: 28 inches high x 18 inches wide x 12 inches expandable to 14 inches deep. 9 lbs. Carry-On Flight Tote Bag: 14 inches wide x 11 inches high x 5 inches deep – 1 lb.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Rockland 4 Piece Softside Upright Luggage Set This deluxe 4-piece expandable luggage set is manufactured with a patented heavy duty EVA-molded hi-count fabric. Made with the very best heavy duty polyester and PVC backing, this luggage set is designed for the traveler on the go and comes with three expandable uprights and a flight tote bag. A variety of colors and patterns are available for ever taste! Carry-on upright: 20"x 12.5"x 7.5" (with wheels) 24-inch Upright: 24"x16"x10" 28-inch Upright: 28"x18"x12" Tote: 14"x11"x5"

Features and Design Telescoping Handle The telescoping handle stows away conveniently and allows for easy maneuvering when extended. Expandable The upright expands an extra 2 inches in depth to maximize your packing capacity. Sturdy Inline Wheels Two sturdy inline wheels allow for easy transport of your belongings.

About Rockland Luggage Since its inception in 1998, Rockland by Fox Luggage has been proudly producing quality luggage and bags for the style savvy traveler. Recognized for its graphic and colorful designs, Rockland prides itself on creating products influenced by current trends in design and fashion. Our products turn heads in a crowd and stand out in the baggage carousel, making it easy for quick exits out the airport. Affordable and travel resistant, Rockland bags are an ideal companion for everything from quick trips to the gym to overnight getaways to extended vacations. Our selection includes: luggage sets (4 piece, 3 piece or 2 piece), hard cases, soft cases, carry ons, rolling backpacks, travel duffels, rolling duffels, cosmetic bags, and kids' backpacks. Over the years, a few Rockland products have been featured in film and television. Their colorful designs make them ideal for an eye catching visual element on screen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Roomy, attractive and lightweight but strong
reviews.reviewText: I was pleasantly surprised as I was worried such a set would be flimsy. they are roomy, and easy to move around But not to Stand alone. I got the black animal print and it looks great. Each piece comes with keys but I would suggest buying your own locks and keys . keys were very light nd work on all pieces but I would not trust the key and locks while traveling on trains or planes. I worried that the inside lining was too thin but I have packed them, Stuffed them and they came through fine . I am on a tight budget and the price was amazing for a 4 piece set with tons of room, expandable tops on the three suitcases and I can tell you the reaction of others seeing them was shock because they do look high end. the only minus really was that I could not get each piece to stand up without me holding it up

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pretty Decent Luggage Set
reviews.reviewText: Bought this luggage set for a job out West that lasted 6 months. Luggage pieces are very roomy as I had to fit clothes for very cold & very hot weather. By the time my heavyweight and lightweight clothes were packed, luggage was pretty heavy as I don't pack light.Wheels worked decently enough and I have to say as heavy as my clothes were, they rolled with no problem. Handles are pretty durable and lasted through the 6 months without any breakage. Zippers could use improving as they held up, but very flimsy. All pieces came back with little to no wear and held up pretty good, I'm hoping the zippers last for a few more trips though.All in All pretty happy with purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I am a total sucker for animal print. The print is so nice in person. I like that they all came nested inside one another. Seems durable. I haven’t had a chance to use them yet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love My Leopard Suitcases!!!
reviews.reviewText: I originally purchased the two piece Rockland leopard set. I loved that little set so much that I decided to purchase the matching 4 piece set and a backpack to use it for my airport travels. It hasn't been tested out at the airport, yet but if it's anything like my two piece set, it will hold up well. Of course, that really depends on the luggage handlers. I know it will be super easy to spot on the conveyer belt because I haven't seen any other luggage in this particular style.Word of warning. Do NOT get the Rockland leopard set that has pink on it. That set is cheaply made and the pull up retracting handle gets stuck A LOT. This set is not like that set. It's better made and much smoother. :))

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Trash. Utter and complete trash.
reviews.reviewText: We bought this set for a six-week trip to Europe. For the price we weren't expecting it to last years. It didn't even survive the first week.Both of the larger checked bags were broken by the time we landed, specifically the handles and frames. The largest suitcase handle and support frame snapped in half inside the suitcase rendering the whole thing unusable. We had to buy a new one for a premium at our destination. The next one broke with the handle stuck down, so while we could still use it, we had to pull it around with a luggage strap which was FAR from ideal on cobbled streets.In general the suitcases are awkward, unbalanced, and heavy. Buy literally anything else besides this. I am livid that I can't get a refund for this garbage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: A great product for the money very pleased

reviews.reviewTitle: A light weight and inexpensive set of luggage.
reviews.reviewText: The luggage is decently built but do NOT use it for heavy stuff. Just clothes.Looking at other more expensive luggage which is heavier and just a bit more durable, I would recommend this set and simply replace it after say 20 trips. I find that buying expensive stuff and expecting it to last for life is wishful thinking. Also forget out warranties and insurance, the claim is typically denied for all kinds of BS excuses. Spend as little as necessary and hope for the best.p.s. I see people always grabbing others luggage ... not mine. :-)
